     C*
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     DJSKHZ
     C                     MOVELPGMNM     DJKOME
     C                     MOVELUSID      DJKOPG
     C                     DELETEJKPP011
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
